{"tid":860462,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[李社長?] 記者爆出內幕 IU與經紀公司的續約條件","createTime":"2018-10-13T11:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T02:45:34.000Z","uid":34643,"like":248,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf05e78444c67c8cc4e33fcebefad2c1364ec96","tid":860462,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:04:20.000Z","msg":"韓歌手IU（本名：李知恩이지은）出道已10年，2005年時她與經紀公司LOEN（現改名Kakao M）7年合約到期，談續約條件時，對外公司僅表示她出自對公司長期的信任和義氣，不另外收簽約金，不過近日有記者在Youtube節目上透露，當時她提出的條件，便是要保障自己團隊員工的工作和薪水。<br />\n<br />\n該位記者透露，IU 2005年與Loen娛樂經紀約將到期時，選擇繼續與自己一路一起打拼的團隊合作，且她不另外收取簽約金，但有2個條件，一是保證續用IU團隊的職員，二是要替這些員工加薪，展現我的人由我來顧的義氣，讓業界人士也相當驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/346/w440h706/20181013/On6s-hmhafir3230264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F346%2Fw440h706%2F20181013%2FOn6s-hmhafir3230264.jpg&h=fb4bb3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/791/w440h351/20181013/la6Z-hmhhnqs2469339.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F791%2Fw440h351%2F20181013%2Fla6Z-hmhhnqs2469339.jpg&h=94660475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/20/w440h380/20181013/vm3P-hmhswim6397614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F20%2Fw440h380%2F20181013%2Fvm3P-hmhswim6397614.jpg&h=3a368043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/422/w440h782/20181013/b40P-hmivixm4960081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F422%2Fw440h782%2F20181013%2Fb40P-hmivixm4960081.jpg&h=8e7b7eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，IU在韓文發音裡是阿一U，她的幕後團隊因此常昵稱她阿會長，一方面是開玩笑，一方面也是感激她對一起工作的員工的照顧之情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.520730.com/file/yulequan/mingxing/20181013/992bca2fc12bb10bf98c9c8e26f8e8ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.520730.com%2Ffile%2Fyulequan%2Fmingxing%2F20181013%2F992bca2fc12bb10bf98c9c8e26f8e8ca.jpg&h=068ef22e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，15年的時候IU經紀人&ldquo;松鼠&rdquo;說：&ldquo;IU出道至今經紀人一直沒有換過，設計師和發型化妝工作人員也沒有變過。&rdquo;，隨即獲網友大贊IU妹子&ldquo;人美心善&rdquo;，&ldquo;真長情&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"fed00867af75ce9112023a2069e723fdb0b0f6f2","tid":860462,"uid":132587,"like":54,"dislike":9,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"佢有無缺點架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2d25ff0a4202e91b25da00c5fd978b50b5d8d4","tid":860462,"uid":2615,"like":50,"dislike":187,"score":-137,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"條件就係要比佢繼續做雞"},{"pid":"1ff0cbfe1c1ddc3e16132ee5bea254b33f00ab2e","tid":860462,"uid":29887,"like":254,"dislike":16,"score":238,"quote":{"pid":"ba2d25ff0a4202e91b25da00c5fd978b50b5d8d4","tid":860462,"uid":2615,"like":50,"dislike":187,"score":-137,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"條件就係要比佢繼續做雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"你老母就雞"},{"pid":"741780c3d087de01590a01276c183e6b12a08215","tid":860462,"uid":61130,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"fed00867af75ce9112023a2069e723fdb0b0f6f2","tid":860462,"uid":132587,"like":54,"dislike":9,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"佢有無缺點架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:17:11.000Z","msg":"上世做左d咩今世先可以做iu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362b31cc3d5351e735076a883344ce680f376889","tid":860462,"uid":88491,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"天使本人"},{"pid":"01cdad6e5b6e9b62a2886996beb75c5977f1ec30","tid":860462,"uid":34643,"like":80,"dislike":4,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"ba2d25ff0a4202e91b25da00c5fd978b50b5d8d4","tid":860462,"uid":2615,"l